What you need to know:

During his heyday as a prolific player, Shikanda made a shock move from Ingwe and crossed over to bitter rivals Gor Mahia, his family opposed the decision and AFC Leopards tried but failed to thwart the moveNow at the helm of Leopards, he talks of his plans for the club and desire to turn the tide and stop the dominance of K’Ogalo in the Kenyan Premier LeagueLeopards’ boss working to ensure players’ well being, sound management and proper marketing strategies to attract sponsors for AFC Leopards to regain its lost glory  